snippet.title: Horror Cartridge Collection - Early Access Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A collection of retro styled games bundled together, experience many forms of horror in a wide array of styles whilst uncovering the mysteries of the old mall that holds them all.
Releasing on Steam Early Access on the 23rd April 2024.

Wishlist and play the Demo on Steam right now
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1873140

Join the official Discord server for updates
https://discord.com/invite/Gr7mCRg

Also available on Itch.io
https://tillion.itch.io/horror-cartridge-collection
